<!--内容 开始-->
<div class="box mt10">
    <div class="map"><img src="${base}/${res}/images/home.png" width="20" height="18"><a href="#">首页</a> >  <a href="${base}/baoliao.jspx">爆料台</a> </div>
    <div style=" clear:both;"></div>
    <div class="details">
                    <div class="article_title">${baoliao.title!}</div>
                    <div class="time">${baoliao.createTime?string('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')}&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;浏览[#if baoliao.readCount ??](${baoliao.readCount})[#else](0)[/#if] 
                         &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:red;">[#if baoliao.state ??][#if baoliao.state == 0]爆料待处理[/#if][#if baoliao.state == 1]爆料处理中[/#if][#if baoliao.state == 2]爆料已解决[/#if][#else]爆料待处理[/#if] </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="article">                   
